---
title: Mexican Fish Burger with Kumara Fries & Smokey Aioli
description: Bite into a flavour explosion with these feisty fish burgers. Our special Mexican seasoning will transform this catch of the day into a smokey fiesta for your mouth! Never fear, the addition of cooling cucumber, tomato and a side of kumara fries will be just the right thing to balance out that flavour kick.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/mexican-fish-burger-09e5be6e.jpg
